                <head>No. 213<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On May 19, 1954, final agreement between the United States and Pakistan regarding
                    United States military assistance to Pakistan was reached. For text of the
                    Mutual Assistance Agreement signed at Karachi on that date, see 5 <gloss
                        target="#t_UST1">UST</gloss> 852. The agreement entered into force
                    immediately.</p>
            </div>
